metadata.name: Couch Surfing
metadata.description:
One Man’s Trash. The imperfections in the world are the things I notice most. That out of place, ‘oh my God, the harrowing idea that someone sleeps here, but it’s so beautiful’ just gets me, and I have to photograph it because I will never witness this moment, this scene, again. And now it is burned in my mind.

Night Work, Los Angeles ~ a series of random images taken during many late nights roaming the city.

Location  
Los Angeles, CA

Date of Capture: Dec 05, 2012
